ol XL";}i:1673;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"1673";s:5:"count";s:2:"60";s:6:"dosage";d:25;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"0.78666";s:4:"name";s:9:"Toprol XL";}i:1674;a:5:{s:10:"id_packing";s:4:"1674";s:5:"count";s:2:"90";s:6:"dosage";d:25;s:14:"price_per_pill";s:7:"0.67825";s:4:"name";s:9:"Toprol XL";}}}}